# Implementation Plan: `@prisma/rest-api-client-generator`

## Overview

This plan covers every file to create and every existing file to modify in order to add the `@prisma/rest-api-client-generator` package to the Prisma ORM monorepo. The generator reads DMMF and emits a typed TypeScript REST API client into the user's project.

---

## Architecture Summary

The package follows the exact same structure as `@prisma/client-generator-ts`:

- `src/generator.ts` — implements the `Generator` interface
- `src/generate-rest-client.ts` — orchestrates code generation and writes files
- `src/type-mapper.ts` — maps DMMF scalar types to TypeScript type strings
- `src/index.ts` — re-exports public API
- `helpers/build.ts` — build entrypoint using `adapterConfig` (bundled CJS + ESM)
- `src/__tests__/generate-rest-client.test.ts` — unit tests

